# Styling Guide

This application uses Tailwind CSS with shadcn/ui components for consistent styling.

## Key Files

- [tailwind.config.ts](mdc:tailwind.config.ts) - Tailwind configuration
- [src/index.css](mdc:src/index.css) - Global CSS styles
- [src/components/ui](mdc:src/components/ui) - shadcn/ui components

## Styling Patterns

1. Use Tailwind utility classes for most styling needs
2. Leverage shadcn/ui components for consistent UI elements
3. Use the `cn()` utility for conditional class names
4. Follow the component's existing styling patterns when making changes

## Theme Configuration

The application supports light and dark themes managed through the ThemeContext with theme toggle functionality.

## Design System

The application follows a cohesive design system with:
- Consistent spacing scales
- Typography system
- Color palette defined in the Tailwind config
- Rounded corners and shadows for depth